snippet.title: Stormgate - Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Meet the Celestial Armada in Stormgate, a new RTS game from Frost Giant Studios. These ancient beings have arrived on Earth where the battle has officiallly begun.

Stormgate is available to pre-purchase now ahead of its July 30 release date. Players can try the game for free from August 13.

#IGN #Gaming #Stormgate
